The paper deals with graphical models and their inference using Belief Propagation, which are topics commonly studied in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) communities. The paper also involves analyzing the performance of the proposed method on different scenarios, which falls under the scope of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
